OL,3,CJersey cost of living higher than
OL,4,CLondon as recommended wage increases
OL,6,FThe Living Wage from 1 Jan 2026:
OL,8,FIt comes after Jersey's Social
OL,9,FSecurity Minister set out plans to
OL,10,Fraise the mandatory minimum wage by
OL,11,F4.5% to #13.59 from next April.
OL,13,FHowever, despite the uplift, it will
OL,14,Fstill lag some way behind the Living
OL,15,FWage.
